snippet.textDisplay: Tribute to forever living Legend, The Great Nusrat Fateh Ali Khan couldn't be better than this. Coke Studio has revived Nusrat Ji's soulful spirit in this solo version. Coke Studio Pakistan has generated a New Version to the song which no one could've imagined could sound so beautiful/heart touching in this Coke Studio Version. Big cheers for Rahat Sahab and especially Momina-who gave the song a new touch/meaning with her soulful feel & melodious singing. It's impossible to sing Nusrat Ji's song in a solo reprise & a female voice, but with a unique melodious Momina voice, the song has evolved in a new genre. Love Momina's part from 2:41 to 3:33 which twists the song in an all new direction and the listener would rather rape the replay button to hear it over n over again. Momina you sang it with such a beautiful feel that I have no Qualms to say this song was written ONLY for you!.....Keep singing & Playing Guys-This show should never stop-Coke Studio Pakistan Forever!
